text:
The impacts of the war in #Ukraine are devastating for women and girls worldwide.

Disruptions in oil & gas supply, staple food commodities and skyrocketing food, fuel & fertilizer prices are widening the gender gap.

Read our latest policy brief: https://t.co/dje3CfsmoP
